Package: kickR
Type: Package
Title: A R Package to scrape and analyze football metrics
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jeffrey Ohene
Maintainer: Jeffrey Ohene <jeffrey.ohene@aol.com>
Description: KickR is your all-in-one R package for football analytics and 
    data scraping. Unleash its power to access and analyze football-related data, 
    encompassing player and team statistics from diverse leagues, including the 
    prominent Big 5 leagues (English Premier League, La Liga, Bundesliga, Serie A, 
    and Ligue 1). With KickR, web scraping football statistics from websites such 
    as FBref is a breeze, while the package also equips you with the tools to 
    effortlessly save and export data to common formats. 
    Excitingly, our upcoming KickR update will introduce features to elevate your 
    football analytics game. From enhancing scouting and performance analysis to 
    identifying similar players based on performance metrics, KickR is your key to 
    deep insights and informed decision-making in the dynamic world of football 
    analytics and machine learning.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    rvest,
    openxlsx
